column2: ALPHA BLACK TO PAPA BEAR. MOUNTAINS HAVE BEEN SWEPT. OVER.
THIS IS CHARLIE BLACK. GET READY FOR EXTRACTION. OVER.
PAPA BEAR THIS IS CHARLIE. ALPHA IS ON BOARD AND WE ARE HEADING FOR HOME. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALPHA. GOOD JOB. MISSION ACCOMPLISHED. WE'LL SEND YOU EXTRACT HELO. HOLD TIGHT. OVER.
I wanna be a mountain ranger
